Package: mumlib
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: mumlib - simple Mumble client library
 Fairy simple Mumble library written in C++, using *boost::asio*
 asynchronous networking framework. Library supports:
 .
 * audio streaming through TCP and UDP channel 
 * text messaging
